.DT
query_money
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_money

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_money -  This method returns the number of coins of a certain type that are in the value of the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_money(string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of coin to look for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the number of coins of that type
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/misc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the number of coins of a certain
type that are in the value of the object.  This is not
a good estimate of value or anything, no idea why it is
here really.  I am sure I had a good reason
at the time :)
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/handlers/money_handlers->create_money_array(), set_value(), adjust_value(), adjust money(), query_money_array(), query_value()

.EP

